    <title>css选择器</title>
    <url>/2020/06/29/css-selector/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="css选择器"><a href="#css选择器" class="headerlink" title="css选择器"></a>css选择器</h1><h2 id="通配符选择器和元素选择器"><a href="#通配符选择器和元素选择器" class="headerlink" title="通配符选择器和元素选择器"></a>通配符选择器和元素选择器</h2><ol>
<li><p>通配符选择器</p>
<p>用 * 表示,选中页面中所有元素,用于设置初始化公共属性</p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">* &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">property</span>: value;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<a id="more"></a>
</li>
<li><p>元素选择器</p>
<p>用html元素名作为选择器,最简单的选择器</p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">E</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">property</span>: value;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="id选择器和类选择器"><a href="#id选择器和类选择器" class="headerlink" title="id选择器和类选择器"></a>id选择器和类选择器</h2><ol>
<li><p>id选择器</p>
<p>唯一性</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#id &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     property: value;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>类选择器</p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.class</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">	 <span class="attribute">property</span>: value;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="属性选择器和伪类选择器"><a href="#属性选择器和伪类选择器" class="headerlink" title="属性选择器和伪类选择器"></a>属性选择器和伪类选择器</h2><ol>
<li><p>属性选择器</p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">E</span><span class="selector-attr">[attribute]</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attribute">property</span>: value;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

</li>
</ol>
<p>   <img src="/2020/06/29/css-selector/1594135373274.png" alt="1594135373274"></p>
<p>   ~ : value之间空格 如: huawei apple</p>
<p>   |: value带有- 如:hua-wei</p>
<ol start="2">
<li><p>伪类选择器</p>
<p>伪类:</p>
<ul>
<li><p>处在一定状态的元素</p>
</li>
<li><p>以冒号开头</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="/2020/06/29/css-selector/1594135581639.png" alt="1594135581639"></p>
<p>伪类如下:</p>
<p><img src="/2020/06/29/css-selector/1594135539927.png" alt="1594135539927"></p>
<p>记忆: LoVe HAte</p>
<h2 id="派生选择器"><a href="#派生选择器" class="headerlink" title="派生选择器"></a>派生选择器</h2><p><img src="/2020/06/29/css-selector/1594135723049.png" alt="1594135723049"></p>
<p><img src="/2020/06/29/css-selector/1594135731085.png" alt="1594135731085"></p>
<p><img src="/2020/06/29/css-selector/1594135742191.png" alt="1594135742191"></p>
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="选择器权重"><a href="#选择器权重" class="headerlink" title="选择器权重"></a>选择器权重</h2><p><img src="/2020/06/29/css-selector/1594135774694.png" alt="1594135774694"></p>
<p>权重是可以相加的</p>
<p>如: div #id</p>
<p>1+100 = 101 权重</p>
]]></content>
